{"tid":2301041,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"佳仔、潘家及港共政府共同獻唱 忘記飛馳","createTime":"2020-11-26T03:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T14:26:04.000Z","uid":295459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d379c039d99ed41733ce0bafdf7fd670f5bd3e2","tid":2301041,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:58:50.000Z","msg":"潘女:<br />\n並沒甚麼 我愛上的 不上我<br />\n點知今鋪 真的輸太多 嘆息奈何<br />\n<br />\n同佳:<br />\n但 綠帽已帶過竟想當我傻<br />\n無忘初心的佢 拿拿救我<br />\n<br />\n潘老母:<br />\n想去台 講兩年 再之後是甚麼<br />\n管賊同埋政協 都好似在唱歌<br />\n<br />\n林鄭:<br />\nRE DO SO RE DO SO 佢出獄護衛多<br />\n將法治淘汰了 香港震動了麼<br />\n龍門在變化 不中又如何<br />\n<br />\n同佳:<br />\nME ME ME 多 最尾最開心嘅我<br />\n花花花花 不需花費麼 我即扮傻<br />\n<br />\n潘老母:<br />\n度度都試下 有天 總會到吧<br />\n為何建制狗派 又靜哂啦<br />\n<br />\n同佳:<br />\n太累 太亂 太害怕 上機先作罷<br />\n你試過日日在豪門 住宅過日那怕悶嗎<br />\n最後界限了求情在嗎 雙腿發麻<br />\n<br />\n港共:<br />\n不送台 不送台 再之後是甚麼<br />\n一百萬唔見了 佳仔脫罪也可<br />\n<br />\n管狗:<br />\nRE DO SO RE DE SO 那資助是甚麼<br />\n口裡無言以對 心中卻是國歌<br />\n屠人若有錯 不坐又如何<br />\n<br />\n港共對潘老母:<br />\nMI MI MI SO 國國國安 經已到<br />\nFA FA FA FA 點樣先算好 你的命途<br />\nMI MI SO RE RE DO DO LA<br />\n如唔信我都算係犯國法"},{"pid":"8ed36e7c7a6d19434817cb171ce95fca5026fe63","tid":2301041,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c7e4d80345f44667dd7cae4ef8797f95ce9765","tid":2301041,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f746b55255ab08b9fd12b92b0643842268295b","tid":2301041,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img sr